8FXsxAu4PsD5dMTmaa-QGztDw/8O33nDgN8SB2amzfrbrTMoC4HEiAaW8r/21" style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; text-decoration: none;" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;div style="overflow: hidden;"&gt;&lt;div style="float: right; margin-left: 12px;"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="203"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iuL.WdmSbEl0/v7/-1x-1.png" alt="As President Donald Trump and President Xi Jinping sit down for their high-stakes summit, a key risk in the US-China relationship is being underplayed: the race to control—and contain—artificial intelligence. On this week’s episode of Trumponomics, host Stephanie Flanders speaks with Council on Foreign Relations Senior Fellow Sebastian Mallaby, who warned that while trade and semiconductors dominate the agenda, AI safety remains a “potentially dangerous missed opportunity” for cooperation between the two powers.Mallaby, author of The Infinity Machine: Demis Hassabis, DeepMind and the Quest for Superintelligence, said the geopolitical rivalry is accelerating AI development even as safeguards lag—increasing the risk of powerful systems falling into the wrong hands." width="203" height="136"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="当唐纳德·特朗普总统和习近平主席坐下来参加高风险峰会时，美中关系中的一个关键风险却被低估了：控制和遏制人工智能的竞赛。在本周的《特朗普经济学》节目中，主持人斯蒂芬妮·弗兰德斯与外交关系委员会高级研究员塞巴斯蒂安·马拉比进行了交谈，马拉比警告说，虽然贸易和半导体在议程中占主导地位，但人工智能安全仍然是两个大国之间合作的“潜在危险的错失良机”。 《无限机器：德米斯·哈萨比斯、DeepMind 和超级智能的探索》一书的作者马拉比表示，地缘政治竞争正在加速人工智能的发展，尽管保障措施滞后——增加了强大系统落入坏人之手的风险。" height="88" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iuL.WdmSbEl0/v7/-1x-1.png" width="131" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin: 0; margin-bottom: 4px; color: inherit; text-decoration: none; font-size: 14px !important;"&gt;播客&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="line-height: normal; font-weight: 700; margin: 0; color: inherit; text-decoration: none; font-size: 18px !important;"&gt;美国必须在人工智能安全问题上与中国接触&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="line-height: 1.4; margin: 0; margin-top: 8px; color: inherit; text-decoration: none; font-size: 16px !important;"&gt; 《特朗普经济学》的最新一集是与&lt;em style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; text-decoration: none;"&gt;《无限机器：德米斯·哈萨比斯、DeepMind 和超级智能的探索》一书&lt;/em&gt;的作者塞巴斯蒂安·马拉比 (Sebastian Mallaby) 的对话，他表示中国人工智能正在缩小差距，这意味着华盛顿不能忽视安全谈判。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;祝周末愉快，阅读愉快。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt; — &lt;em style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;Silvia Killingsworth，《彭博周末》和 James Tarmy，《彭博追踪》&lt;/em&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 style="font-size: 24px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: 700; padding-top: 12px; border-top: 1px solid; margin-top: 40px;"&gt;更多来自彭博社&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul style="margin-top: 24px; padding-inline-start: 24px;"&gt;&lt;li style="font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.4; font-size: 16px;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/QgNETInro82HDrqdnp-tmL_vgzMWDYrYJrrxLBelKDGWAEzHxGviq3o15WPaxap0BnYNzkdQN7LxMDBbing5vDyZprd-eOXrLJB8oWnFqzegG5W6tzxcRRKhIsuhKejQXNHH_ArtNrSywb1q1s8UZYnDbUW5x7ax8VzHo9oNQJ_rT8-nLNPt5BOW6S-mIBoClf24yOHbCZIRELmaE-gAjWgRebYEJinPmTe0wOvS4pkXQ8jj54vx7UH3l33FLHosSf0AKBk_C7HQeceEUpSgv8SM-7rgcmsHjS7BdJ9V74ClrIvopj-ij02ydbJX8t4yCj9SBFklsyobKGXtfmAglDWz3TuZVj_bYAaZTMt5NeEAnj4e3Ne9j-mfU5c2TfMCyexJgzQfHoYo8RMjtwqaC7m2Vsldl_2m6K2HZa5ORmpYM4c6N736Y2gR5nDu9ni-B57Atq6N64iDhbniuIMH/LHjV_d5XKUsAx66fCZKyLW0_jPk4qZoa/21" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="color: #00e; font-size: 16px;" target="_blank" title="彭博周末"&gt;彭博周末，&lt;/a&gt;提供精彩想法和开放式问题&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.4; font-size: 16px;"&gt;思考未来的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/KJsPOJXRWgrEDRgw0D_8zWMnkR_lXiJVZ2ehujbpK_Zlpo4UYmctxP6WO15QCEh8FQ_yotnqrPb-ESUECe5iCvCYHzzdvFOs-vrvXs40o303ZGF2kpk-dxlvGUQRMzvCRMUmvuzaRfuWysOU6JMd2F3JfTMzB3U2tsnlVN9K_4QdoO_BfEXdD1tofRU-KM4a