ef="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/SMMB0qCAp8klRjaNMjraPWbgkk1e3tAK7ef1QTBKaRo0amaEHenktErNnyD3yImSuFcymgFmARCE857b7CdD4FESrupIGJ4s6NjasRmSpuh5t_0lOHns4-XvZYATseMx0mftfU8hE0hex5QR9wHeZyfj2g4wcZ9U2mmDnaED1TJs95hWHyVQL5WFnPA6YU0jTSpIoRx34ylWBNMWB3Vu-Qgh6kvBS3DxbnN3NS-ucpcz0bwfd8dkhNJGh78rdEd7qB2nCA14xGyoPKAQvaLUFe8oxd02bw/SDuG9OK5vrLEvyzG9wPWR9OL0Yc5c0VH/21" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="农业解决方案 |托皮有机物"&gt;Toopi Organics&lt;/a&gt;的弗朗索瓦·杰拉德 (François Gérard) 表示：“遗憾的是，战争局势对我们来说是一件好事。”该公司将从学校和节日收集的人类尿液转化为有助于植物生长的细菌饲料。他说，自2月底以来，销量增长了约四分之一，由于供应充足，价格保持稳定。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt; “我们到处都是尿液，”杰拉德说。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;由于美国和伊朗对霍尔木兹的封锁还没有结束，化肥中断预计将持续存在。长期冲突可能意味着收成减少和&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/N0tO7RQ6QZUAPS3tj-CFz2108HT2ali5AvysvbGxbqDssZiL9f6aj9tQZqqRc7YYde8WhfAEHY2DCjcDugPJ7_4zeB0BQRViV_moqxKLkmQyZNsWdvz75Ot85IhbGQr6TZ9LxehZGehWx-CqGh3K4Kqg3-9YYKVm-RsqZjxhl-1_01xBgI4Bpys5c4VaMvt3CH60tC1DLjGztD_AOEiVz7n8RiL6RQRSOuOxYLaKaquE3Joj_dof1UWtSIrAkUoETDGOkmWDcZTl0UovwIEF8sKXG7fwTvr1Um4xDv-mJu_6iXLz1L7KsDq3ISNQlRTaRJTlvt2QoeHhQSckphGW-JfOGhkmthTzdzrg62a4s4dJkO84lOVLJ-EiVdNsHxRVhmq4vuXbirqhDZJLz6GZX4pwHvd2SG_g0EnzY1gtVXarruHqrczjWi03XhnBDT8gzh8iQMu4rGPK5Taf-xm823ZQPbw7-XEWiEsbLk2a-Pm-sPpSH0iNU8bwv6IAeCWzn9i5d5XY78jboCs57SD2ETXaHT7EmXWSnWAQtOyhWtXnCi6Kblwmb0gTjk_52EcVsw/N1iXkw2fyeYExsee-JzOa3-bv-Bbi2Dc/21" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="伊朗战争如何撼动食品供应链"&gt;杂货价格上涨&lt;/a&gt;。联合国警告称，另外 4500 万人可能面临&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/I2qtPWwooecGgVkVmQRZUA9Y09HIcpTJY_xTHQd_U8l7D90DWjK8fPt-dt3PlROsNB96sYg1S4KQ5IOKff38IQzRdz3e6kRZJ2QEYO0OPqdEKDCjWi7rzvH5lEIIt3l-EmmffsyLz2Y98J4_ARly0GOcealyhw8PFQcvewG8P--67c24s6PtwPlfD5dbZT7MLqR7VyVYsHl0tskt5YSazqO5VP-Emr-CVHgEtGlDSr04xz_MvJK9BJWXZs_wivx1wT6NUZJZYtG-9ipsVjBssni8Nu5wL-wSC5i13_ACmoRVgYRvHh2fHXSV2Go9FGCUS3z